WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.107
We operate in a boundaryless organizational environment where technological acceleration,

00:00:04.107 --> 00:00:08.214
cultural friction, and human sustainability constantly converge. The traditional rulebooks

00:00:08.214 --> 00:00:12.321
of management have been rendered obsolete. We demand strict practical

00:00:12.321 --> 00:00:16.427
relevance to your career and the complex social systems you

00:00:16.427 --> 00:00:20.534
navigate daily. You are here to develop a performance of

00:00:20.534 --> 00:00:24.641
understanding. You have not truly learned these concepts until you

00:00:24.641 --> 00:00:28.748
can actively apply, analyze, and create new knowledge to solve

00:00:28.748 --> 00:00:32.855
the undefined challenges waiting for you.
